{"analytics_identifier":"OT1415","base_path":"/government/organisations/infected-blood-compensation-authority","content_id":"80fc3a6c-b2c4-471d-be00-e3639169d9f8","description":"The Infected Blood Compensation Authority (IBCA) will deliver the Infected Blood Compensation Scheme, which will provide financial compensation to victims of infected blood on a UK-wide basis. The Scheme responds to the recommendations made by the Infected Blood Inquiry in its second interim report, and the earlier study into compensation by Sir Robert Francis KC.","details":{"acronym":"IBCA","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Infected Blood Compensation Authority (IBCA) will deliver the Infected Blood Compensation Scheme, which will provide financial compensation to victims of infected blood on a UK-wide basis. The Scheme responds to the recommendations made by the Infected Blood Inquiry in its second interim report, and the earlier study into compensation by Sir Robert Francis KC.</p>\n</div>","brand":null,"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"Infected Blood<br/>Compensation Authority"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/infected-blood-compensation-scheme","title":"Infected Blood Compensation Scheme"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/infected-blood-compensation-authority-ibca-register-your-interest-to-help-shape-the-service","title":"Get in touch with us"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/infected-blood-interim-compensation-payment-scheme","title":"How to access existing support schemes and interim payments"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/infected-blood-how-to-access-additional-support","title":"How to get additional support"},{"href":"https://ibca.org.uk/","title":"Infected Blood Compensation Authority website"}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priori